  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 20.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第20课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "One Man in a Boat.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "独坐孤舟。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why is fishing the writer's favorite sport?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么钓鱼是作者最喜欢的运动？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Fishing is my favorite sport.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "钓鱼是我最喜欢的运动。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I often fish for hours without catching anything.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我常一钓就是几个小时，却什么也钓不到。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "But this does not worry me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "但这并不使我烦恼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Some fishermen are unlucky.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有些垂钓者运气不好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "Instead of catching fish, they catch old boots and rubbish.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他们钓不到鱼，反而钓上旧靴子和垃圾。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "I am even less lucky.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我的运气甚至更差。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "I never catch anything, not even old boots.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我什么也钓不到，连旧靴子也没有。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "After having spent whole mornings on the river, I always go home with an empty bag.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在河边耗费整个上午后，我总是提着空袋子回家。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "You must give up fishing, my friends say.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你必须放弃钓鱼，”朋友们说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "It's a waste of time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“这是浪费时间。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "But they don't realize one important thing.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "但他们没有认识到一件重要的事。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "I'm not really interested in fishing.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我对钓鱼其实并不感兴趣。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "I am only interested in sitting in a boat and doing nothing at all.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我只对坐在船上无所事事感兴趣。"
      }
    }
  ],
